title: Celteric - Nova Fractal In The Mix (Goa Trance Mix)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

In The Mix is a special edition of Nova Fractal released and unreleased works, mixed by DJ Celteric and published by Neogoa Records and Ektoplazm! Download mix in high audio-quality here: http://www.neogoa.net/nova-fractal-in-the-mix/

Tracklist:

01 - Nova Fractal - Through Our Senses (144 BPM)
02 - PharaOm - Cellar Door (Nova Fractal Remix) (144 BPM)
03 - Nova Fractal - Autopsy (145 BPM)
04 - Nova Fractal - Blindsight (145 BPM)
05 - Nova Fractal - Common Cold (Unreleased Mix) (145 BPM)
06 - Sky Technology - Back To The Future (Nova Fractal Remix) (145 BPM)
07 - Nova Fractal - Perception (146 BPM)
08 - Nova Fractal - Perplexed (Unreleased Mix) (146 BPM)
09 - Nova Fractal - Reality Of Life (146 BPM)
10 - Sky Technology & Nova Fractal - Dark Energy (Versus Mix) (146 BPM)

More Neogoa Records at:

http://www.facebook.com/neogoarecords
http://www.twitter.com/neogoarecords
http://www.instagram.com/neogoarecords
http://www.youtube.com/c/neogoarecords

More DJ Celteric at:

http://djcelteric.com/

http://soundcloud.com/celteric/
